window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A Frogmorton Farm short story from the best-selling author of the Chronicles of St Mary's. Perfect for fans of Sarah Addison Allen, Kristen Ashley and Genevieve Cogman.</p> <p>It's Christmas time again, and all is not well at Frogmorton Farm.</p> <p>Jenny and Russell's daughter, Joy, is growing up. Not quickly enough as far as she's concerned but far too quickly according to Russell.</p> <p>Father and daughter are at odds, and suddenly the outlook is very dark indeed. That is until Thomas comes to the rescue.</p>"; 
